parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the door actuator can cause the doors to malfunction, leading to difficulties in entering or exiting the vehicle, which can be a safety concern, especially in emergency situations.
symptoms: The doors fail to latch or unlock
the doors stick or become jammed
the doors do not respond to the door lock/unlock switch
the doors do not open or close properly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the front driver door actuator can cause the door to jam, making it impossible for the driver to enter or exit the vehicle, which can lead to serious life-threatening situations in emergency situations.
symptoms: The front driver door actuator jams
the door does not open
the door does not close
the door is stuck in a partially open or closed position
difficulty opening or closing the door.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power door lock actuator can cause the doors to malfunction, leading to inconvenience, security risks, and potential safety hazards, especially if the doors become stuck in an open or locked position.
symptoms: The doors do not lock or unlock properly
the doors lock or unlock randomly
the doors make a grinding or clicking noise when attempting to lock or unlock
the door lock switch does not respond
the doors are stuck in an open or locked position.
